{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-00124/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-00124"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:01:24"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["high key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man applies shaving cream to his face."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-00124","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-00124"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/canvas/1/46cd0277-64b2-4223-b125-37bb03744baa","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T13:43:39.064Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds Woodcock is introduced through a montage of his morning routine. From the start, we see how fastidious he is in all he does. Every step of the process involves attention to detail. Furthermore, it’s clear that his persona and appearance are carefully curated, not entirely natural.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:23.04044117647063,60.01102941176459,258.38602941176475,182.4816176470588"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/canvas/1/ffd7171f-96f2-4011-9d6e-f1fa84469355","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T13:44:16.380Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The camera cuts to “the most demanding man,” who is applying shaving cream in a marble-walled bathroom. The first step in the routine, at least as the audience sees it here, is his application of shaving cream to his face. Though we don’t see him actually shaving, this act highlights how he strives to remove any imperfections from his life.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:640.1580882352941,346.7977941176469,525.2647058823527,521.1507352941178"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/canvas/1/efe066c4-675b-415d-ac49-9fcb1132f441","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T13:44:51.048Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The veins of the marble act as a physical representation of Reynolds’ complexity as they join and separate in random patterns. Despite being regimented, we will soon learn that Reynolds is prone to whimsical reactions, not unlike the random pattern of the marble that flanks him in the bathroom. His face also takes up a large part of the screen, establishing not only his centrality to the story but also his all-consuming nature, which the film highlights as the narrative progresses.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00124/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1210.4117647058822,129.50735294117635,527.2720588235295,647.3051470588235"}}}]}]}]}